      • getAutofillValue

        public java.lang.Object getAutofillValue(java.lang.Object[] fieldValues,
                                java.lang.Integer triggerIndex)
        Get the autofill value. This will first try to get the autofill value based on the trigger index (if specified) before falling back on the address configuration of how to autofill the desired field.
        Parameters:
        fieldValues - the values that correspond to the fields that were passed into the constructor.
        triggerIndex - the field that triggered this autofill call.
        Returns:
        the autofill value.
